dct_title_s: North Italy to accompany The handbook for travellers
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. "The numbers affixed to the names of places refer to the routes in the handbook--in which they are described." Originally issued folded in cover 15 x 10 cm., with cover title: Map of North Italy. Also issued to accompany A handbook for travellers in northern Italy. London : John Murray, 1858.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published by John Murray, Albemarle Street, June 1st 1858.
